\p
\v 6 Now brothersÂŠ114343 and sistersÂŠ114343, I applied theseÂŠ114341 things to myselfÂŠ114346 and ApollosÂŠ114348 for yourÂŠ114350 sakes, so that through us you all might learnÂŠ114355 this: âNot beyondÂŠ114358 what is writtenÂŠ114361,â so that no one would be puffed up in favour of one againstÂŠ114370 the otherÂŠ114372,
