\v 10 Another might be given the ability to do miraclesÂŠ118015, and someone else given prophecyÂŠ118019. Another might be given ability to distinguishÂŠ118022 spiritsÂŠ118024, and someone else given the ability to speak other languages, and to yet another the ability to translateÂŠ118033 languages.
\v 11 However it's the one and the same spirit behind all those thingsâdistributing them individually to each personÂŠ118046 as the spirit decides.
\s1 One body with many parts
