\v 17 If \add your\add* whole body was an eye, how could \add you\add* hearÂŠ118171? \add But then,\add* if \add your\add* whole body was an ear, how could \add you\add* smellÂŠ118177 \add anything\add*?
\v 18 Actually, \nd GodÂŠ118183\nd* has placed every part in our bodies \add exactly\add* where he wantedÂŠ118194 to put them.
\v 19 If it was all just one part, how could it be a bodyÂŠ118204?
