\p
\v 1 Even if I could speakÂŠ118404 in humanÂŠ118403 languages as well as the languages of \add God's\add* messengersÂŠ118407, butÂŠ118409 didn'tÂŠ118410 loveÂŠ118408 \add others\add*, then I'd \add just\add* be like a noisy gong or a clanging cymbalÂŠ118416.
