\p
\v 1 Aim to \add show\add* loveÂŠ118629, andÂŠ118631 eagerly strive for spiritualÂŠ118633 \add things\add*âespecially the ability to prophesyÂŠ118637,
\v 2 because anyoneÂŠ118649 speaking another language isn'tÂŠ118643 speaking to \add the\add* peopleÂŠ118644, but to \nd GodÂŠ118648\nd*, because no one understands \add it\add*, but they're speaking \add about\add* spiritualÂŠ118652 mysteriesÂŠ118655.
\v 3 However, anyone who's prophesyingÂŠ118658, speaksÂŠ118660 to \add the\add* peopleÂŠ118659 for their instruction and encouragement and comfort.
\v 4 Anyone who's speakingÂŠ118667 in another language instructs themself, butÂŠ118672 when \add people\add* prophesyÂŠ118673, they're instructing the \add whole\add* assemblyÂŠ118674.
