\v 20 BrothersÂŠ118959 andÂŠ118959 sistersÂŠ118959, don'tÂŠ118960 be childishÂŠ118961 in your thinking. You all can be like infants with respect to \em evil\em*, butÂŠ118970 \add in everything else\add*, be matureÂŠ118972 in your thinking.
