\v 23 SoÂŠ119022 if the wholeÂŠ119027 assemblyÂŠ119026 gathered togetherÂŠ119024 at the sameÂŠ119030 placeÂŠ119030 and they all spoke in other languagesÂŠ119035, and then some inquirersÂŠ119040 or unbelieversÂŠ119042 came in, wouldn't they say that you're all crazy?
